**Step 6**: Combine the four inequalities using the triangle inequality.
The line of thought is to use `add_le_add` repeatedly to combine `h8, h9, h10, h11`. This is done by proving intermediate inequalities step-by-step, which are then combined. The key insight is that `eLpNorm (T' (fвӮҒ + fвӮӮ + fвӮғ + fвӮ„))` is less than or equal to the sum of `eLpNorm (T' fбөў)` terms, which in turn are bounded by the sum of the right-hand sides of `h8, h9, h10, h11`.

```tactics
have h12 : eLpNorm (T' (1 вҖў fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.re (f x) : NNReal) + (-1 : NNReal) вҖў fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.im (f x) : NNReal) * RCLike.I)) 1 (ОҪ.restrict G) вүӨ (c / p) * eLorentzNorm' (fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.re (f x) : NNReal)) p 1 Ој * (ОҪ G) ^ p'вҒ»В№.toReal + (c / p) * eLorentzNorm' (fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.im (f x) : NNReal) * RCLike.I) p 1 Ој * (ОҪ G) ^ p'вҒ»В№.toReal := by
  have h13 : eLpNorm (T' (1 вҖў fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.re (f x) : NNReal) + (-1 : NNReal) вҖў fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.im (f x) : NNReal) * RCLike.I)) 1 (ОҪ.restrict G) вүӨ eLpNorm (T' (1 вҖў fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.re (f x) : NNReal))) 1 (ОҪ.restrict G) + eLpNorm (T' ((-1 : NNReal) вҖў fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.im (f x) : NNReal) * RCLike.I)) 1 (ОҪ.restrict G) := by
    have h14 : eLpNorm (T' (1 вҖў fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.re (f x) : NNReal) + (-1 : NNReal) вҖў fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.im (f x) : NNReal) * RCLike.I)) 1 (ОҪ.restrict G) вүӨ eLpNorm (T' (1 вҖў fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.re (f x) : NNReal))) 1 (ОҪ.restrict G) + eLpNorm (T' ((-1 : NNReal) вҖў fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.im (f x) : NNReal) * RCLike.I)) 1 (ОҪ.restrict G) := by
      have h15 : eLpNorm (T' (1 вҖў fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.re (f x) : NNReal) + (-1 : NNReal) вҖў fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.im (f x) : NNReal) * RCLike.I)) 1 (ОҪ.restrict G) = eLpNorm (T' ((1 вҖў fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.re (f x) : NNReal)) + ((-1 : NNReal) вҖў fun x вҶҰ (RCLike.im (f x) : NNReal) * RCLike.I))) 1 (ОҪ.restrict G) := by rfl
