- `hpp' : p.HolderConjugate p'` is the conjugate exponent condition
- `T_meas : вҲҖ {f : Оұ вҶ’ рқ•Ӯ}, (hf : MemLorentz f p 1 Ој) вҶ’ AEStronglyMeasurable (T f) ОҪ` ensures that $T$ maps measurable functions to measurable functions
