Simplify `eLpNorm (T (1 вҖў (algebraMap в„қ рқ•Ӯ вҲҳ gвӮҒ))) ...` to `1 * eLpNorm (T' gвӮҒ) ...` and `eLpNorm (T (RCLike.I вҖў (algebraMap в„қ рқ•Ӯ вҲҳ gвӮӮ))) ...` to `вҖ–RCLike.IвҖ– * eLpNorm (T' gвӮӮ) ...`. This uses `eLpNorm_smul` and properties of `norm` on `в„қвүҘ0` functions.

