Then, `1 вҖў gвӮҒ(x) = a(x)`, 
`-1 вҖў gвӮӮ(x) = -a(x)`, 
`I вҖў gвӮғ(x) = I вҖў b(x)`, 
`-I вҖў gвӮ„(x) = -I вҖў b(x)`.

The sum is `a(x) - a(x) + I вҖў b(x) - I вҖў b(x) = 0 + 0 = 0`.

This is still not correct. We need to use the real and imaginary parts of `f(x)`.

