The sum is `RCLike.re (f x) - RCLike.re (f x) + I вҖў RCLike.im (f x) - I вҖў RCLike.im (f x) = 0`.

This is still not correct. We need to use `RCLike.ofReal` and `RCLike.I`.

Let `f(x) = a(x) + I вҖў b(x)` where `a(x), b(x) вҲҲ в„қ`. Then `gвӮҒ(x) = a(x)`, `gвӮӮ(x) = a(x)`, `gвӮғ(x) = b(x)`, `gвӮ„(x) = b(x)`.

